column5: I'm probably late... Or my word's don't matter... But I do all just in hopes I can die... My family found out that I want to kill myself from my ex's son and now they are high alert... And said if I killed myself they all will to... Ugh... /': now I have to suffer until either someone kills me or I have a heart attack I can't take this horrible world anymore!!! Horrible people everywhere!!! And I'm one of them!!! I need to die before I hurt someone!!!! God someone help me!!!!!
That's it...? Any position?
I'm better now...... It's been pretty mad....... What would you recommend..?
Look... You don't know me... And I'm not trying to be rude.... But I lost everything.... From my kids.... Friends... Relationships.... I can't take it anymore!!!
It doesn't matter okay... I'm finished........ /: I would like a yes or a no at least....
Hey!
I'll join you both...

But sometimes I truly want to do those thing's... I have self control... I mean I've picked a knife up once or twice... But stopped... I do want to see a therapist but where do I look?? I don't have money at the moment at least... I just wanna be happy and enjoy life you feel? Thank you for those words...
Thank you I'm trying üôÇ I appreciate you responding just scared...
Thank you thank you! I'm here all day lol
I feel it........ /:
I'm calm a little... And just every single mistake I've ever made piling up... Overflowing... Sigh...
Oh god... I'm sorry... /': I need help... Bad...
Don't seem....
A little yes...
Worse than ever... Sorry...
True lol who knows man who knows @-@
